In conclusion, I plead guilty to the offense of driving whilst disqualified. I accept full responsibility for my actions and express my sincere remorse for any harm caused. I am committed to improving myself and taking appropriate measures to prevent any similar offenses from happening again. I respectfully request the court's leniency and consideration in determining an appropriate sentence.

